# GSAP SCROLL ARCHITECTURE

Only activates when GSAP was flagged in geometry model.
If GSAP not required: skip entirely.

GSAP is a physics engine. Model the scroll system before writing a single line.

---

# GSAP CONFIDENCE GATE
## Run before any ScrollTrigger code.

Scroll container clearly defined?               +20
Pin duration deterministically calculable?      +20
Layout stable (no overflow / transform issues)? +20
Start/end derived from geometry (not guessed)?  +20
Responsive behavior defined?                    +20

