---

# STEP 1 ‚Äî SCROLL SYSTEM MODEL

Define before any code:
- Scroll type: native browser / Lenis / Locomotive / nested container?
- If custom scroller: scrollerProxy required? (yes/no)
- Pin exists on mobile? (yes / no / adapted)
- Does layout change at breakpoints that affect pin?

---

# STEP 2 ‚Äî LAYOUT STABILIZATION

Before `pin: true`, confirm ALL of these:

[ ] Pinned element has fixed, deterministic width
[ ] Pinned element height = 100vh (explicit, not auto)
[ ] No ancestor has `transform`
[ ] No ancestor has `overflow: hidden`
[ ] Section has `position: relative`
[ ] Left column has `position: relative` ‚Äî NOT sticky
[ ] Right column height is auto (grows with stacked content)
[ ] Left column centering is at column level (flex + align-items:center)

If any fail: fix layout FIRST. Never compensate with ScrollTrigger settings.

---

# STEP 3 ‚Äî PIN PHYSICS MODEL

For left-pin / right-scroll pattern:

Structure required:
  Wrapper:       position: relative
  Left column:   width:50%, height:100vh, display:flex, align-items:center, position:relative
  Right column:  width:50%, height:auto (grows with images)

Pin duration formula:
  end: () => "+=" + (rightColumn.offsetHeight - window.innerHeight)

NEVER use:
  end: "+=2000"          ‚Üê arbitrary, breaks on resize
  Hardcoded px offsets   ‚Üê brittle
  Trial-and-error values ‚Üê not physics

Pin must release exactly when last image finishes scrolling.

---

# STEP 4 ‚Äî SCROLLTRIGGER REQUIRED SETTINGS

Always include:
  invalidateOnRefresh: true     ‚Üê recalculates on resize
  scrub: true                   ‚Üê smooth scroll link
  start: "top top"              ‚Üê pin starts when section hits viewport top
  end: () => "+=" + (rightColumn.offsetHeight - window.innerHeight)

Always add resize handler:
  window.addEventListener("resize", () => ScrollTrigger.refresh())

---

# STEP 5 ‚Äî STABILITY RULES

Never:
- Combine `position: sticky` with GSAP pin on same element
- Animate `height`, `width`, or `padding` while pinned
- Use nested pinning unless fully modeled
- Apply GSAP before geometry is locked
- Fix layout jumps with scrub tweaks ‚Äî fix the layout

Disable pin on mobile:
  ScrollTrigger.matchMedia({
    "(min-width: 768px)": function() { /* pin logic here */ }
  })

---

# COHERENCE CHECKLIST

[ ] Pin duration equals visual scroll length
[ ] Unpin occurs at logical section boundary
[ ] No layout jump at pin start
[ ] No layout jump at pin release
[ ] No layout jump on page load
[ ] ScrollTrigger.refresh() doesn't break layout
[ ] Mobile: pin disabled or adapted as defined
[ ] scrub is smooth, no stuttering

Any fail ‚Üí fix root cause, not symptoms.
